### BitDMX: Research & Integration
**BitDMX** = Our visionary STARK-augmented implementation of **BitVMX**.

**Foundational Papers** (all publicly available):
- **BitVM: Compute Anything on Bitcoin** ‚Äì Robin Linus (ZeroSync), Dec 2023
- **BitVM2: Bridging Bitcoin to Second Layers** ‚Äì Robin Linus et al., 2025
- **BitVMX: A CPU for Universal Computation on Bitcoin** ‚Äì Sergio Demian Lerner, Ramon Amela et al., arXiv:2405.06842 (May 2024) ‚Üí [Whitepaper](https://www.bitvmx.org/files/bitvmx-whitepaper.pdf)

**What we add**:
- zk-STARK proofs instead of SNARKs (transparent + post-quantum)
- Ethical AIR constraints
- Chia sidechain anchoring
- Full integration with Starknet Cairo contracts

This enables deterministic oracles on Bitcoin without soft-forks ‚Äî a first.

